"{\"uid\": \"thenorthlines.com-indias-scientific-sleep-plan-for-paris-2024-olympic-success\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Good Night's Sleep is Crucial for Paris Success  With the Paris Olympics only a few months away, the Indian contingent is leaving no stone unturned in their preparations.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 103, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9842075877590508, \"rank\": 0.015474544405128472, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time ever, they will have an expert sleep advisor accompanying them to help optimize their sleep schedules.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Monika Sharma, an experienced sleep consultant, will analyze the challenges athletes face in sleeping well during such a high-pressure event and design customized strategies.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monika_Mann\", \"score\": 0.9038399371068606, \"rank\": 0.10576608067475081, \"text\": \"Monika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monika_Mann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monika_Mann\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting adequate, restorative sleep is crucial for peak performance according to studies.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything from reaction times to strength and endurance can improve with proper sleep.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, factors like jet lag, stress, and the lively atmosphere in the Olympic Village can disrupt rhythms.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999974434104, \"rank\": 2.556387808535752e-09, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Sharma has already begun meeting athletes worldwide to understand individual needs.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She plans to educate them on sleep importance and possible obstacles in Paris like heat.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999960933959211, \"rank\": 3.906619227309504e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Innovative solutions like temporary sleeping pods and travel kits are also being provided.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes will be able to take short naps to supplement any compromised sleep.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This scientific approach aims to give India's athletes an edge by removing elements of luck and unpredictability tied to poor sleep.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9935286236951736, \"rank\": 0.0038040640207391723, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Past Olympic gold medalist Neeraj Chopra has struggled with insomnia before major events due to various distractions.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neeraj Chopra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The advisor and new facilities should help our representatives maximize recovery and energize focused efforts on the field.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A good night's rest could boost metrics like reaction times by over 10% according to research.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While skills are high level, marginal gains through optimized rest may provide just the boost needed for top performances.\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"India is leaving no stone unturned in chasing Paris gold through strategic sleep management.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9935286236951736, \"rank\": 0.0038040640207391723, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 1749, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999960933959211, \"rank\": 3.906619227309504e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thenorthlines.com is a leading digital platform covering and disseminating the news, views and allied information on evolving public policies and responses pertaining to Indian subcontinent and its neighbourhood with a particular focus on the north India region.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_subcontinent\", \"score\": 0.9939913269597362, \"rank\": 0.002964221891941749, \"text\": \"Indian subcontinent\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_subcontinent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_subcontinent\"}, {\"begin\": 2046, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9935286236951736, \"rank\": 0.0038040640207391723, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 Northlines.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Powered byRodiex Services LLP\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": []}]}"